{"tid":1390691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寫「我愛香港」 譚小環免費請正義年輕人食腸粉套餐","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T09:49:48.000Z","uid":25468,"like":207,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"911b557c2509ed76e7844fe46ce9fed6a5627d0c","tid":1390691,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190730/s00009/9e5ef229bf10bfb9bb09a3765ec1829b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190730%2Fs00009%2F9e5ef229bf10bfb9bb09a3765ec1829b.jpg&h=d12bcd09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂引來的風波至今持續，近日有網民在社交平台發文，表示見到年紀很小的前線抗爭者，寧願用錢購買保護裝備，也不肯留來買飯吃，結果民間發起各類支援運動，不少食肆表示會為「小朋友」提供免費食物，譚小環與老公蔡強榮經營的「渣哥 一九九六」是其中一間，並在facebook公布詳情：<br />\n<br />\n【通告】<br />\n【細路，唔好餓壞身體】 <br />\n由2019年7月31日，明天起<br />\n每天由10:00-21:00<br />\n凡正義的年青人（目測似就得勒（喇））<br />\n光臨渣哥任何一間分店<br />\n（銅鑼灣，德福，東涌）<br />\n<br />\n用黃色Memo紙寫著&rdquo;我愛香港&rdquo;<br />\n（店面有紙，筆提供）<br />\n<br />\n交給店員，就等於1張免費食券，渣哥就會免費請你食1個腸粉套餐，每人每次可以最多2份。<br />\n**本店保留任何最終決定權<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言「感謝 香港人食肆」，亦有人說：「全力支持！我會過嚟幫襯亦會寫下-我愛香港！免費食券就不用給我。留畀有需要嘅香港年輕人！感謝你對香港嘅愛 祝生意興隆」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67226710_2381436845267676_5607931673036455936_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_eui2=AeFhhzF7Nu-sS0fvL-fQ0biFoH5YzahAMkt3HxuHtsF1sbKAb8Z3_f8x4v9tWqGq6hA1Au5ZMeZ-usSmS6NzKehYt8SF8wB2n-PjvAfCUtlGNw&amp;_nc_oc=AQnquYDoaEy2w7aEjx_iPLzgGXK1xDqoaZ5IRNCMS8dJpKuTnF59DtOMjXKdZr60Cns&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=9ad1aed178bedcf550ee62d0e250a39c&amp;oe=5DA5E62C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67226710_2381436845267676_5607931673036455936_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_eui2%3DAeFhhzF7Nu-sS0fvL-fQ0biFoH5YzahAMkt3HxuHtsF1sbKAb8Z3_f8x4v9tWqGq6hA1Au5ZMeZ-usSmS6NzKehYt8SF8wB2n-PjvAfCUtlGNw%26_nc_oc%3DAQnquYDoaEy2w7aEjx_iPLzgGXK1xDqoaZ5IRNCMS8dJpKuTnF59DtOMjXKdZr60Cns%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D9ad1aed178bedcf550ee62d0e250a39c%26oe%3D5DA5E62C&h=80804387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67156387_2381439461934081_4739387276017008640_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_eui2=AeE_5-EWX2ACmWX2e_2ggRgtGzUO1wYwWKrHCc8BCuTlS29zXXUhUIVrPboMqkNOWNxEwVI8-5DJQd0SrKMCNVumI2Lz5LVz2jZNcuj7WASehw&amp;_nc_oc=AQkUoDZ96CdO33wgI66owb_pZiAHI4sgMuSGWwDFs0AuhWJRIwbz8W39IWvMFQziuyU&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=a2c876cff2d79d7d9397786c4490864b&amp;oe=5DA870B5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67156387_2381439461934081_4739387276017008640_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_eui2%3DAeE_5-EWX2ACmWX2e_2ggRgtGzUO1wYwWKrHCc8BCuTlS29zXXUhUIVrPboMqkNOWNxEwVI8-5DJQd0SrKMCNVumI2Lz5LVz2jZNcuj7WASehw%26_nc_oc%3DAQkUoDZ96CdO33wgI66owb_pZiAHI4sgMuSGWwDFs0AuhWJRIwbz8W39IWvMFQziuyU%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Da2c876cff2d79d7d9397786c4490864b%26oe%3D5DA870B5&h=f28d68dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98326fb7963417727a09ed0581e179185029ee81","tid":1390691,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:07:17.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnRPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=48ed6d33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。"},{"pid":"2b4b6fd17417bfa36c789d3f81afe76e5bdea316","tid":1390691,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d78199d0c2c7f70c085c5dad5983bd6fc3d6c49","tid":13906